---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
const metadata = { title: 'Terms of Service | Winning Plumber' };
---
<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 mx-auto lg:px-8 lg:py-20 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="font-bold font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-tighter tracking-tighter mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-4xl dark:prose-invert mt-8">
      <p>Welcome to <strong>Winning Plumber</strong>. By using our service, you agree to these terms regarding your professional booking URL setup.</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8">1. Service Description</h2>
      <p>Winning Plumber provides technical setup and redirection for professional vanity URLs (yourname.winningplumber.com) designed for plumbing professionals.</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8">2. One-Time Payment</h2>
      <p>The $99 fee is a one-time setup and licensing fee. There are no monthly recurring SaaS taxes for the lifetime of the redirect service provided at setup.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
